---
---

<section id="about">
  <div class="inner">

    <div class="bio-block">
      <div class="bio-text">
        <p class="eyebrow">About Case</p>
        <h2>Craftsman. Builder.<br />Father of the Workshop.</h2>
        <p>
          Case Vollink has been building things with his hands his entire life. Based in Texas, he has spent years constructing playsets, sheds, and custom homes for families across the DFW Metroplex — gaining a reputation for showing up, doing it right, and leaving people with something that lasts.
        </p>
        <p>
          Now Case is channeling that same craft into his own workshop — turning raw lumber into furniture, built-ins, and one-of-a-kind pieces that make a room. If you can imagine it, he can build it.
        </p>
        <a href="#contact" class="link-cta">Work with Case &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="bio-image">
        <img src="/shed.jpg" alt="Custom shed built by Case Vollink" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <blockquote class="testimonial">
      <svg class="quote-mark" width="36" height="28" viewBox="0 0 36 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M0 28V17.6C0 12.587 1.493 8.48 4.48 5.28C7.467 2.08 11.627 0.373333 16.96 0.159999L17.92 3.2C14.613 3.62 12.053 4.9 10.24 7.04C8.533 9.07333 7.68 11.5 7.68 14.32H14.72V28H0ZM19.04 28V17.6C19.04 12.587 20.533 8.48 23.52 5.28C26.507 2.08 30.667 0.373333 36 0.159999L36.96 3.2C33.653 3.62 31.093 4.9 29.28 7.04C27.573 9.07333 26.72 11.5 26.72 14.32H33.76V28H19.04Z" fill="currentColor"/>
      </svg>
      <p>"Add a testimonial here — ask a happy client for a sentence or two about the experience and quality of work."</p>
      <cite>— Client Name, Location</cite>
    </blockquote>

    <div class="services">
      <p class="eyebrow">What I Do</p>
      <h2 class="services-heading">Services &amp; Capabilities</h2>

      <div class="service-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/>
              <path d="M3 9h18M9 21V9"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Outdoor &amp; Structural</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Playsets</li>
            <li>Sheds &amp; Storage Structures</li>
            <li>Rough Framing</li>
            <li>Trim Carpentry</li>
            <li>Doors &amp; Exterior Work</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M20 7H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v10a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z"/>
              <path d="M16 3H8a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v2h12V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Built-ins &amp; Cabinetry</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Custom Built-ins</li>
            <li>Closets &amp; Storage</li>
            <li>Entertainment Centers</li>
            <li>Kitchen Islands &amp; Cabinets</li>
            <li>Mini Bars</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/>
              <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/>
              <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Furniture &amp; Originals</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Bed Frames &amp; Bedroom Sets</li>
            <li>Tables &amp; End Tables</li>
            <li>Hall Trees</li>
            <li>Cutting Boards <span class="ships-badge">Ships Nationwide</span></li>
            <li>Custom One-of-a-Kind Pieces</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    padding: 7rem 2rem 6rem;
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .inner {
    max-width: 1160px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--oak);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* ── Bio block ── */
  .bio-block {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .bio-text h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .bio-text p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  .link-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--forest);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--oak);
    padding-bottom: 0.1rem;
    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .link-cta:hover {
    color: var(--forest-dk);
    border-color: var(--forest-dk);
  }

  .bio-image {
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.13);
  }

  .bio-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ── Testimonial ── */
  .testimonial {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--forest);
    color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 3rem 3.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .quote-mark {
    color: var(--oak);
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    display: block;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .testimonial p {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
  }

  .testimonial cite {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--oak-lt);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  /* ── Services ── */
  .services-heading {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .service-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 2rem 1.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: box-shadow 0.25s, transform 0.25s;
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 10px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .card-icon {
    color: var(--forest);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .service-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .service-card li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .service-card li::before {
    content: '–';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--oak);
  }

  .ships-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(44, 95, 45, 0.1);
    color: var(--forest);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .service-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .bio-block {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .bio-image {
      order: -1;
    }

    .service-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .testimonial {
      padding: 2.5rem 1.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>
